### **CR-01: Rider Portal — XSS Vulnerability (WORST ISSUE)**  
**Severity:** 🔴 **CRITICAL (10.0)** — **UNTOUCHED BY REFACTOR**  
**File:** `rider/app.js:526-572` (renderAllOrders)  
**Status:** ❌ **STILL VULNERABLE**  

**The Problem:**  
The `escapeHtml()` function exists (lines 83-91) but is **NOT USED** in the two `innerHTML` assignments that render order data. All Firebase order data (customer name, address, order ID) is inserted directly without escaping.

**Vulnerable Code:**
```javascript
// Line 551-564: Unassigned orders displayed to riders
unassignedList.innerHTML += `
    <div class="order-card-premium">
        <div class="order-id-chip">#${o.orderId || id.slice(-6)}</div>   // ❌ NO ESCAPING
        <h3 class="rest-name">Drop-off: ${o.address || 'Unknown'}</h3>    // ❌ NO ESCAPING
        ...
    </div>`;

// Line 577-597: Active delivery info
dashboardActiveView.innerHTML = `
    <h3>${cName}</h3>                         // cName = customerName — ❌ NO ESCAPING
    <p><i data-lucide="map-pin"></i> ${cAdd}</p>  // cAdd = address — ❌ NO ESCAPING
    ...
`;
```

**Attack Scenario:**  
1. Customer places WhatsApp order with malicious name: `<img src=x onerror=stealCookies()>`
2. Bot writes this to Firebase `orders/{orderId}/customerName`
3. Rider views order in portal → XSS executes in rider's browser
4. Attacker steals rider's Firebase auth token → full account takeover
5. Attacker can now view all orders, customer PII, rider location, accept/deliver orders fraudulently

**CSP Makes It Worse:** `rider/index.html` CSP has `'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval'` → XSS payload executes without any bypass needed.

**Remediation (URGENT — 1 line fix per location):**
```javascript
// Fix 1 (line 551-564):
unassignedList.innerHTML += `
    <div class="order-card-premium">
        <div class="order-id-chip">#${escapeHtml(o.orderId || id.slice(-6))}</div>
        <h3 class="rest-name">Drop-off: ${escapeHtml(o.address || 'Unknown')}</h3>
        ...
    </div>`;

// Fix 2 (line 577-597):
dashboardActiveView.innerHTML = `
    <h3>${escapeHtml(cName)}</h3>
    <p><i data-lucide="map-pin"></i> ${escapeHtml(cAdd)}</p>
    ...
`;
```

**Impact:** Complete compromise of all rider accounts → data breach, order fraud, reputation damage.

