### **H-05: No Rate Limiting on Bot Orders**  
**File:** `bot/index.js:371-569`  

Bot accepts unlimited orders from any WhatsApp number. Spammer could flood system with fake orders (DoS, database bloat).

**Fix:** Implement per-phone rate limiting in session data:
```javascript
const orderTimestamps = {};
// When order placed:
if (orderTimestamps[phone] && Date.now() - orderTimestamps[phone] < 60000) {
    return sock.sendMessage(sender, { text: "Too many orders. Please wait 60 seconds." });
}
orderTimestamps[phone] = Date.now();
```

